        {
            "title": "美國企業縮減招聘計畫 年迄今宣布增加的崗位數創2009年以來同期新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據Challenger, Gray &amp; Christmas公佈的數據，美國雇主在9月份縮減了招聘計畫，宣布的裁員數量也有所減少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">9月企業宣布計畫新增117,313個崗位，較上年同期下降71%，計畫招聘人數創下2011年以來同期最低。周四發布的報告還顯示，與往年相比，季節性招聘計畫顯著放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年1月至9月期間，美國雇主宣布計畫增加近20.5萬個崗位，創2009年以來同期最低水平。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c50acf94-61cd-38d1-9c12-a7bfdee6ddbf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，上月企業宣布裁撤54,064個崗位，同比下降近26%，且低於8月份公佈的85,979個。裁員計畫並不一定會很快演變為真正的裁員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Hiring Plans, Job-Cut Announcements Drop in Challenger Report</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%AE%E6%B8%9B%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BF%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%B4%97%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%89%B52009%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E5%90%8C%E6%9C%9F%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-112600195.html",
