        {
            "title": "全球晶片製造商在人工智能熱潮中創紀錄上漲 市值增加2000億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 全球晶片製造商市值飆升，投資者爭相佈局人工智能領域，這成為科技股持續飆升至歷史高位的最新跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行業正被人工智能公司的一波利好消息所席捲，包括OpenAI通過在員工股份出售中創下5000億美元估值紀錄，並與韓國多家晶片製造商達成協議；另有報導稱英特爾正洽談將Advanced Micro Devices Inc.納入客戶名單。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博計算，這波漲勢已使費城半導體指數與亞洲晶片股指數的總市值在最新交易日中飆升逾2000億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-db8cb61c-75d4-3ec6-af32-b04d85155a45-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受OpenAI合作消息推動，周四韓國晶片股領漲，並推動韓國Kospi指數漲至紀錄高位。SK海力士股價飆升10%，三星電子上漲3.5%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ArkkdQY73IX2klvZtCmMTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/20fc26919dc94bedbdb947bfbdae31f5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師指出，此輪牛市主要由「害怕錯過」（FOMO)心理驅動，投資者普遍忽視了人工智能領域可能形成泡沫的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「科技股漲勢毫無減弱跡象，仿佛重力不存在一般，逆風被輕易拂去，每條人工智能新聞都引發狂熱情緒，」Vantage Markets分析師Hebe Chen表示，「泡沫論調雖未消散，但主導市場的顯然是FOMO心理。這股漲勢看似能自我維持，直到即將公佈的第四季度財報可能迫使市場回歸現實。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期股價上漲導致晶片製造商估值飆升：彭博亞洲晶片指數當前交易價格約為預期未來收益的19倍，而SOX指數當前交易價格為收益的27倍，逼近2024年創下的歷史高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Global Chipmakers Add $200 Billion in Record Rally on AI Frenzy</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Edwin Chan、Bernadette Toh.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%95%86%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%86%B1%E6%BD%AE%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A02000%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-085436041.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-02 20:35:50",
