        {
            "title": "曼徹斯特猶太教堂發生襲擊後 英國首相臨時改變行程回國召開緊急會議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在曼徹斯特一座猶太教堂外發生車輛和刀具襲擊事件後，英國首相基爾·斯塔默縮短了在丹麥參加一場歐洲峰會的行程，返回英國並將主持召開政府緊急委員會會議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大曼徹斯特警方在X平台發文稱，上午9時30分剛過，警員接報趕往曼徹斯特克倫普索爾區希頓公園希伯來會堂猶太教堂處理該事件。警方稱，四名民眾因被刺傷及車輛衝撞傷勢正接受急救人員救治，一名疑似襲擊者被持槍警員擊中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次襲擊發生於猶太教贖罪日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一位官員表示，當時正在哥本哈根參加歐洲政治共同體會議的斯塔默，現已啟程返回英國，將主持緊急事務委員會會議。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-55d08e40-a469-3ce9-b553-f728bcd232d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Starmer to Hold Emergency Meeting After UK Synagogue Attack</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B9%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%BE%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%9B%9E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-110310586.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-02 20:10:57",
