        {
            "title": "歐盟擬提議將鋼鐵進口關稅稅率提高一倍至50%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 根據彭博看到的一份提議草案，歐盟計畫將鋼鐵進口關稅上調至50%。此舉將使歐盟關稅稅率與美國保持一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟現行臨時性鋼鐵保障機制規定，當進口配額用儘後，對多數進口產品徵收25%關稅。該機制將於明年到期，歐盟正著手制定更長效的替代方案，計畫下周公佈新機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據草案，負責歐盟貿易事務的歐盟委員會計畫將該關稅稅率提高至50%，「以最大限度降低貿易轉移風險」。當進口量達到特定配額時，將適用更高稅率。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99faa87c-13db-3240-aa2d-4e1f40a25221-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該計畫根據歷史平均值為特定產品類型設定配額。歐盟委員會還尋求獲得權力，為不同門檻設定各國特定配額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU to Propose Doubling Tariff Rate on Steel Imports to 50%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E6%93%AC%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E9%8B%BC%E9%90%B5%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E7%A8%85%E7%8E%87%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98-%E5%80%8D%E8%87%B350-094726032.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-02 18:22:15",
