            "title": "擬「Full Pay」最多2億入市搏成「新舖王」　李根興：沒銀行肯借錢畀我",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"舖市專家李根興擬今季再動用最多2億「full pay」入市。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"307\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/H2ZHxgDb8nmbXiOEH.u2Hw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/b75e6b31354c2df7dfabd26aa6eccde0\" width=\"546\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:546px\">舖市專家李根興擬今季再動用最多2億「full pay」入市。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>在零售與商舖市場不景氣下，曾言</span><span>「身體健康，財務糟透(Physically well, financially terrible)」的盛匯商舖基金創辦人李根興接受報章訪問，他就</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>旗下基金被傳不穩時表示，現階段「已經沒有銀行肯借錢給我」，但他並未選擇撤退，反而計劃在逆市「full pay(全款支付)」出擊，動用1億至2億元資金於本季度入市，目標購入5至10間街舖，伺機成為市場見底之際的「新舖王」。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"在零售市場不景氣下，本港舖市面臨相當打擊。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"553\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.5aEWxdchpRs9rcD8.lASA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3MztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/tl/am730_578/5706945bbe2dadc19be965e511ecc5ba\" width=\"926\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:926px\">在零售市場不景氣下，本港舖市面臨相當打擊。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>銀行閂水喉   改變策略</span></span></span></span></span>Full Pay</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>李根興提到，早年大開水喉的本地銀行，近期大幅收緊對工商舖的貸款審批，不僅削減額度，批核程序也更趨嚴謹。他直言，銀行目前對純粹買舖收租的投資行為態度保守，除非企業為擴展業務、開設分店或裝修營運而申請貸款，否則難以獲批。盛匯基金在舖市高峰時購入的部分物業現錄得帳面虧損，使其融資環境困難。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3ea96cd0-3ccd-3865-a8ec-088b64aa8678-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>在融資受阻下，李根興表示將改變策略，擬在今年下半年購入的商舖一律先以「全款支付(</span><span>full pay)</span><span>」，再等待明年初銀行擁有新預算額度時，才申請貸款套現。他預期，屆時工商舖按揭或會稍為鬆動，推算貸款利率約為最優惠利率加2厘。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">澄清<span><span><span><span><span>基金運作良好  有新投資者加入</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>同時，他亦</span><span>計劃於年底前動用1億至2億元購入具潛力街舖，而且為保持資金流動，基金年初至今已售出12個舖位，套現約2.3億元，距離全年出售20間舖、套現3億元的目標不遠。他強調，目前基金淨負債比率維持於5%，攻守兼備。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>對於外界認為盛匯基金不穩，李根興澄清，基金運作一直良好，現時可動用逾億元現金入市，且有新投資者加入。他透露，自2016年以來，基金累計買入132間舖位，已售出91間，目前仍持有逾50間香港街舖。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>另外，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>面對當前困境，他仍以幽默態度看待，笑言回答朋友問候時總說：「我身體健康，但財政糟透！」並樂觀補充：「這總好過『財政健康，但身體糟透』！」</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/擬-full-pay-最多2億入市搏成-新舖王-李根興-沒銀行肯借錢畀我/605029?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/擬-full-pay-最多2億入市搏成-新舖王-李根興-沒銀行肯借錢畀我/605029?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/擬-full-pay-最多2億入市搏成-新舖王-李根興-沒銀行肯借錢畀我/605029?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%AC-full-pay-%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A2%E5%84%84%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E6%90%8F%E6%88%90-%E6%96%B0%E8%88%96%E7%8E%8B-053700918.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-02 14:35:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
}